(410, 1, '2016-03-03 10:42:10', '2016-03-03 10:42:10', '<h1>Terms &amp; Conditions</h1>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2>Legal Notices and Terms of Use</h2>\r\nWelcome to this website Gadnews, which is owned and operated as part of the Gadnews network ("Gadnews") and includes our website. Gadnews maintains the Site as a service to its visitors, which is a subject to the following terms and conditions concerning the use of the Site ("Terms of Use"). When you use the Site, you accept the Terms of Use; if you do not agree to the Terms of Use you should not use the Site. Gadnews reserves the option to edit content on the Site and these Terms of Use periodically without preliminary notice.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2>Use of Content on the Site</h2>\r\nYou may view, download, and print contents from the Site subject to the following conditions: (a) the content may be used solely for informative purposes; and (b) the content may not be modified or changed in any way. You may not publish, distribute, prepare derivative works, or otherwise use the content other than as explicitly permitted herein.\r\n\r\nYou may not use any framing techniques to hide any trademark, logo, or other proprietary information (including images, text, page layout, or form) of Gadnews without the written consent of Gadnews. You may not use any meta tags or any other "hidden text" utilizing Gadnews'' name or trademarks without the express written consent of Gadnews. You may not use any Gadnews logo or other proprietary graphic or trademark as part of the link without express written permission.\r\n\r\nYou do not receive any ownership rights to any content in the Site. Any unauthorized use discontinues the permission or license granted by Gadnews.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2>Reviews, Comments, Communications, And Other Content</h2>\r\nYou may submit comments and provide other content so long as the content is not obscene, illegal, harassing, or defamatory and so long as the content does not invade the privacy or infringe the intel